sources.description:
Wild and Wicked Early California...where men fought to protect their lands, their lives...and their ladies! 
In Mexican California, a land feud erupts and murder is committed when rich landowner Don Domingo reneges on an earlier verbal promise made by his father to grant to the tenant Melo family a piece of land.

Director: Allan Dwan
Writers: Beatrice A. Dresher, Miguel Padilla, Joseph Lejtes
Stars: Cornel Wilde, Yvonne De Carlo, Raymond Burr, Lon Chaney Jr.
Genres: Adventure, Drama, Western
